/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[uspCreateMedicalTables]    Script Date: 09/02/2022 5:03:10 pm ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO

SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE procedure [dbo].[uspCreateMedicalTables]
as 
Begin 
	IF Not EXISTS (SELECT * FROM sys.objects WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID(N'[dbo].[tblMedicalData]') AND type in (N'U'))
	CREATE TABLE [dbo].[tblMedicalData](
		[Patient id]		bigint		,
		[Employee Name]		nvarchar(50),
		gender				nvarchar(10),
		[In Military]       nvarchar(12),
		military_service	bit			,
		dob					Date		,
		[Birth Month]       int			,
		zipcode				bigint		,
		employment_status	nvarchar(12),
		education			nvarchar(12),
		marital_status		nvarchar(10),
		children			int			,
		ancestry			nvarchar(25),
		avg_commute			decimal(8,2),
		daily_internet_use	decimal(8,2),
		available_vehicles	int			,
		disease				nvarchar(30)			
	) ON [PRIMARY]
end
GO
